    <item>
      <title>印度股市暴跌，因选举结果远低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-s-stock-futures-rise-as-investors-await-election-result</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市周二下跌，初步计票结果显示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的执政党在全国大选中难以赢得多数席位，而此前的出口民调显示，莫迪有望获得压倒性胜利，这一结果令人震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-s-stock-futures-rise-as-investors-await-election-result</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 01:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：欧洲股市因交易员担心美国数据疲软而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对美国经济健康状况的担忧与对美联储早期放松政策的更强预期，欧洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 22:36:25 GMT</pubDate>
